<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <%= javascript_importmap_tags %>
  <title>Home</title>
</head>
<body class="m-0 p-0">
<div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-cover bg-bottom w-full" style="background-image: url('<%= asset_path('farshotbest.jpg') %>');">
  <div class="rounded-full w-80 h-80 mt-20 md:h-96 md:w-96">
    <%= image_tag 'logolight.png', alt: 'Main splash image', class: 'rounded-full' %>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center mt-10">
    <div class="text-5xl flex justify-center gap-16 py-3 text-white">
      <a href="https://instagram.com/fullsendwaxing?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=" target="_blank">
        <i class="fab fa-instagram h-10 w-10 text-white hover:scale-125"></i>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/fullsendwaxing/" target="_blank">
        <i class="fab fa-facebook-square h-10 w-10 text-white hover:scale-125"></i>
      </a>
      <a href="https://vm.tiktok.com/ZTdCK6Uqn/" target="_blank">
        <i class="fab fa-tiktok h-10 w-10 text-white hover:scale-125"></i>
      </a>
      <a href="https://venmo.com/code?user_id=1964786585698304640&created=1700151778.773841&printed=1" target="_blank">
        <%= image_tag 'logo-venmo.svg', class: 'h-10 w-10 text-white hover:scale-125 venmo-icon' %>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<section>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-content">
        <h2>Dedicated to the turn.</h2>
        <p>
          We're on a mission to redefine your snowboarding and skiing experience,
          blending expertise with a laid-back vibe.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-between gap-2">
          <div class="hidden md:block w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'dylan-thielsen.JPG', alt: 'Dylan Stegman split-boarding on Mt Thielsen in Central Oregon', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'alec-lassen.JPG', alt: 'owner splitboarding in Lassen Volcanic National Park', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:block w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'nh-thielsen.JPG', alt: 'Matthew Davenport split-boarding on Mt Thielsen in Central Oregon', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-content">
        <h2>We're all about the ride.</h2>
        <p>
          Our story kicks off with a heartfelt love for snow sports and a profound respect for the mountain landscapes.
          We've finely tuned our skills to become your ultimate choice for snowboard and ski maintenance.
          Our commitment to excellence fuels our attention to the nitty-gritty, tailored to your unique style.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'mountain-view.jpg', alt: 'customer splitboarding the eastern sierras', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-content">
        <p>
          We're eco-warriors at heart, rocking biodegradable waxes to keep our mountain playgrounds as fresh as the powder you love.
          And guess what? We've got your back, offering pickup and delivery right to your doorstep.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-content">
        <h2>Tuning services.</h2>
        <p>
          We're all about delivering next-level expertise with a commitment to eco-friendliness.
          Our convenient pick-up and delivery service brings top-notch gear and service right to your doorstep.
          Let's ride, and make the mountain experience yours!
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-between gap-2 sm:mt-2.5 mt-10">
          <div class="hidden md:block w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'edgework1.jpg', alt: 'Dylan Stegman split-boarding on Mt Thielsen in Central Oregon', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'closebest.jpg', alt: 'owner waxing and tuning board', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:block w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'closework1.jpg', alt: 'Matthew Davenport split-boarding on Mt Thielsen in Central Oregon', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-content">
        <h2>Ski and board repairs.</h2>
        <p>
          ðŸ”§ Ptex Repairs: Say goodbye to those unsightly base gouges and scratches.
          Our meticulous Ptex repairs seamlessly blend with your equipment, ensuring smooth, uninterrupted glides down the slopes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-content">
        <p>
          ðŸ”ª Edge Repairs: Cracked or damaged edges can spell trouble on the mountain.
          Let us restore your edges to their former glory, providing you with precision control and confidence on every turn.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-center gap-2 sm:mt-2.5 mt-10">
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'farshot1.jpg', alt: 'owner waxing and tuning board', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-content">
        <h2>Know what people use on your hard-earned gear.</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-between gap-2 sm:mt-2.5 mt-10">
          <div class="hidden md:block w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'productbest.jpg', alt: 'best products in use', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'products1.jpg', alt: 'products in use', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:block w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'productclose.jpg', alt: 'products we use closeup', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>
          At our waxing company, we take great pride in the quality and sustainability of our products.
          We exclusively use Purl Wax for our waxing services, a renowned, eco-friendly brand known for its exceptional performance and durability on the slopes.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-row justify-between gap-2 sm:mt-2.5 mt-10">
          <div class="hidden md:block w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'purllogo.png', alt: 'best products in use', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:block w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'logocolorlight.png', alt: 'products we use closeup', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'swixlogo.png', alt: 'products in use', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-content">
        <p>
          We prioritize eco-friendliness in all aspects of our operations. Purl Wax shares our commitment to
          environmental stewardship. Their products are formulated with eco-conscious practices, ensuring minimal impact on the natural surroundings
          we all cherish.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-white flex flex-row justify-center gap-2 sm:mt-2.5 mt-10">
          <div class="hidden md:block w-1/3">
            <%= image_tag 'POW.png', alt: 'products we use closeup', class: "w-full object-cover rounded-lg" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-content">
        <p>
          Rest assured, when you choose our services, you're not only getting top-quality performance, but you're also supporting a sustainable and
          environmentally conscious approach to winter sports maintenance.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white py-6">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
      <div class="mb-4 md:mb-0">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@yourcompany.com" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">info@yourcompany.com</a></p>
        <p>Phone: <a href="tel:+1234567890" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">(123) 456-7890</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-4 md:mb-0">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Location</h2>
        <p>City of Operation: <span class="text-blue-400">San Jose, California</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-4">
      <p>&copy; <span id="year"></span> Full Send Waxing. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
<script>
    document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
</script>
</body>
</html>